:: either run away [run] {"position":"175,450","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:purple)+(bg:black)[You begin to run as fast as you can, the faster you run the louder the screaming gets. You look behind you but end up losing your balance and fall on the ground. ](text-colour:red)+(bg:black)[ [[ The screaming stops.]]] 


:: faster [faster] {"position":"300,325","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:purple)+(bg:black)[You stumble upon an old abandoned cabin, you take a moment to breathe. You begin to walk closer and examine the building. After a few minutes you hear screaming , the screaming is coming from behind you (text-colour:red)+(bg:black)[[either run away]] or (text-colour:blue)+(bg:black)[[go into the cabin.]]
]


