:: keep walking [COOL] {"position":"775,225","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:#74c0fc)+(bg:black)[You get  closer to the lake and find a rock to sit on, You take a deep breath and relax.  You decide to wait by the lake until sunrise. ]


